{"tid":613412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞新王古天奴警告沙拿放棄皇馬 應加盟巴塞","createTime":"2018-04-01T16:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T16:22:29.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"87219f97275bcc9dec111d15e081215feac6561f","tid":613412,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"PHILIPPE COUTINHO has reportedly warned Liverpool star Mohamed Salah to snub Real Madrid and join him at Barcelona.<br />\n<br />\nThe Egyptian has been in stunning form for the Reds since his summer switch from Roma and he bagged his 37th goal of the season to sink Crystal Palace today.<br />\n<br />\nSalah&rsquo;s prolific debut campaign has sparked speculation around his future, with a number of European heavyweights believed to be circling.<br />\n<br />\nReal Madrid remain the hot favourite for his signature, with club president Florentino Perez plotting a major squad overhaul this summer.<br />\n<br />\nBut fierce rivals Barcelona could look to hijack Real&rsquo;s bid as they aim to continue their dominance in La Liga."},{"pid":"ba763f55a3758a149f445e18176dd90464a5105b","tid":613412,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"source or police"},{"pid":"e8dafef4b86959a7c619e4722831d9e3616cbb4e","tid":613412,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"邊有位 買防中即食中堅算啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下年基沙文加盟"},{"pid":"eb3b9dca357545aa7f4690f6662a3f05b7e50ee6","tid":613412,"uid":2033,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/003036_1f2012dde3990f21d8bcfbea3a24bb48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F003036_1f2012dde3990f21d8bcfbea3a24bb48.png&h=cdba41e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e3dc3303641fae3539f852f57d750d0089d60e